# DOCS_TEST: example_003

query error
-- Only matches the exact capitalization
SELECT id, title FROM movies_exact_idx WHERE PHRASE(title, 'The Matrix');
----
db error: ERROR: Scalar Function with name phrase does not exist!
Did you mean "<slt:ignore>"?


